title: Danna ga Nani wo Itteiru ka Wakaranai Ken 2 Sure-me
synopsis: The Tsunashi couple is as lively and offbeat as ever. Hardcore otaku shut-in Hajime and workaholic office lady Kaoru still get themselves into hilarious situations thanks to both their own eccentric natures and the bizarre group of friends surrounding them.
